prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card front, flat 2D illustration. A lighthearted cartoon scene featuring the two people from the reference photo. Lao Lao, on the left, is wearing a light blue sweatshirt and has a joyful, laughing expression as she stands triumphantly on a small winner's podium labeled "#1". Jordan, on the right, wearing a tan hoodie, is on a slightly lower "#2" podium, playfully pretending to be sad and sulking with a funny pout. Both are holding video game controllers. The background is a clean, solid pale cream color. In the center, below the characters, the text "Happy Birthday to my favorite person to lose to" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script in a dark charcoal color. The overall style is clean, modern, with simple shapes and a focus on the humorous interaction.
